To install PERFect package use:

library(devtools)
install_github("katiasmirn/PERFect”)

Main functions: 
PERFect_sim — simultaneous PERFect filtering algorithm 
PERFect_perm — permutation PERFect filtering algorithm

Data sets:
data(mock2)
data(ravel)

Algorithms and data are described in: 

Smirnova, E., Huzurbazar, H., Jafari, F. “PERFect: permutation filtration of microbiome data", Biostatistics, 2018, kxy020, https://doi.org/10.1093/biostatistics/kxy020

